title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: The Friday Feast features Aaron Gleeman in studio chatting baseball for several segments, then the final hour is dedicated to the "numbers game," analyzing each player on the Vikings roster into 2019....in this case, players wearing jerseys 11-20 were up for prognostication.
